data.description: Alert to Investors or anyone familiar with the Hamilton Area!!!  The Seller is very motivated.  This is a super cute remodeled home that looks a little lived in.  With a little handyman work, by work I mean paint job,  this is an ideal opportunity and property for someone that wants to get into the desirable Hamilton 21214 zip code.  The home was fully remodeled in 2020 and there was a basement waterproofing job done in 2023.  Look past any minor issues and you will see the home as the cute and cozy home you see in the photos.  The Seller is looking at any and all offers as they come in so be the first to submit your offer....
